    <note>Jiang(3) Ruhui (zi) [26745] All Mingzhou Jiang(3) were members of this lineage, which established itself in Mingzhou with the move here by Jiang(3) You [16184]. Ruhui held office and was a contemporary of Yuan(1) Xie, which would make him a probable great grandson of You and Ruhui must be a zi rather than mingzi. Yuan Xie, WJ, 21.1a-3b (wife, born Pan(1), who died in 1219 at age 73). Not indexed in CBD.</note>
